        "body": "## Summary\n- Add control-plane Tranche A+B scaffolding for contracts, schemas, registries, queues, reports, artifacts, dashboards, and ledgers.\n- Add Tranche B registries: `registries/schemas.registry.json`, `registries/validators.registry.json`, and `registries/policies.registry.json`.\n- Add a read-only CI gate at `.github/workflows/control-plane-validate.yml` that runs only `node scripts/validate_openclaw_control_plane.cjs` on `pull_request` and pushes to `main`.\n- Extend `scripts/validate_openclaw_control_plane.cjs` to enforce registry existence, path resolution, policy required fields (`id/version/status/decision/applies_to/reason`), allowed status values (`active|deprecated|experimental|blocked`), workflow contract/validator registration checks, secret-like config checks, and PHI marker checks for artifacts.\n\n## Verification\n- `node scripts/validate_openclaw_control_plane.cjs`\n  - Result: `PASS` (`findings: []`)\n\n## References\n- Conversation: https://app.warp.dev/conversation/ac14c3af-59df-48d6-961b-57f906c660ab\n\nCo-Authored-By: Oz <oz-agent@warp.dev>\n",
